      "message": "I assumed that we would not change the shard number too often.\n\nThe alternative will be we try to update a row, if no row is updated, insert one.\n\nOne special case is when 2 requests compete with inserting rows with the same primary key, then one of them will fail, then we should catch that error and do update again.",
